descriptionHtml:
This is a preset I've made that I decided to post here for no apparent reason. I use CBBE Bodyslide for the body and the armor is a light Stalhrim armor mod made by justice123. (https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/71675/) 


[b]The requirements are here (That I know of)[/b]

- KS Hairdos    https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/68311
- Spectral Shades-Eyes   https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/12307/

[b]Optional (but recommended)[/b]

- Fair Skin Complexion   https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/51602
author: Shotokan8988
